VTP - VIRTUAL TRUNKING PROTOCOL
---------------------------------
- CISCO PROPRIETARY PROTOCOL
- AUTOMATES VLAN PROPAGATION
- EASIER TO MANAGE VLAN
- SWITCHES SAVED THEIR STARTUP CONFIG TO A FLASH MEMORY
- VTP TURNED ON BY DEFAULT AND IN SERVER MODE, CANNOT BE TURNED OFF


Routers saved configuration in a start-up config and saved in NVRAM (non-Volatile RAM)


