2. Password
3. version
4. Trunk?

Verify:
sh int trunk
sh int <interface name> switchport



! To change a VTP server to client mode, follow these steps:

Access the switch in EXEC mode.
Enter VLAN configuration mode:
Switch# vlan database

Set the VTP domain name (if needed):
Switch(vlan)# vtp domain <domain_name>

Change the VTP mode to client:
Switch(vlan)# vtp client

Exit VLAN configuration mode:
Switch(vlan)# exit



